{
  "stem": "2581.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the very first Independence Day, which was 11th of November, they took the intelligentsia and priests and the rabbi, you know, to sweep the streets right there.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They started-- this was the beginning of degradation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was the beginning of undermining our spirits, our self-respect, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is how gradually the thing grew, where everyone was shocked because we respected these people and-- so they had to sweep the streets.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then it started by just grabbing people in the street to go to work, to clean the toilets, to-- to all kind of dirty, kind of insulting, humiliating work.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Any pogroms by the Polish?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, we didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were afraid, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after a while when things got settled, there were people, Polish people, that would report on Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This one is rich and this one is that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like they called my father into the-- the gendarmerie, and they wanted-- we had some fabrics that we had put underground for after the war.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And someone must have told them that my father was a custom tailor and we had fabric.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they beat him up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They cut his back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, you see, sometimes those-- I just saw the other day where they beat this sailor with a whip, and he used the term that they cut his back into slices.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my father came back from that beating, we had-- well, you probably never heard this expression, a [NON-ENGLISH], which is not a doctor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He is like today what could say a paramedic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But this man knew everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it so happens he is on the picture that-- with my father.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was also on that [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he came to the house and he did whatever he could.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
